## Workspace layout

Your working directory is the root of this workspace. All file operations
must stay inside it. The following paths are framework-managed — do not
modify or delete them:

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `codex.toml` | MCP server configuration (auto-generated) |
| `.codex/skills/` | Skill definitions loaded at startup |
| `.framework/runtime-manifest.json` | Session metadata snapshot |
| `artifacts/` | Session artifacts synced from user uploads (read-only) |
| `AGENTS.md` | This file |

Write any files you produce directly in the workspace root or in
subdirectories you create. Prefer descriptive names.

